text: Callum O'Brien (born 4 November 1982) is a New Zealand professional squash player. He reached a career high of 61 in the world. He represented his country in the Commonwealth Games in 2006 ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand male squash players Category:Squash players at the 2006 Commonwealth Games Category:Commonwealth Games competitors for New Zealand
